_sText:
Hey,

Here's my 3rd map.

For this one I tried to make a little bit more technical map, although it is still a map that can be ran at high speed.

There's 21 stages, a bonus and a lobby.

Don't mind the light bugs, I haven't found a solution yet.

This is the ported version of bhophamelscgo. I did the port myself.
Thanks to Saspatoon for pointing out a trigger bug.

I hope you guys will enjoy running and routing this map.

Have a great day, 

Fur
